Rhodia Designates Independent Expert to Report on Solvay Offer

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-06T22:48:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/rhodia-designates-independent-expert-to-report-on-solvay-offer.html
Rhodia SA (RHA)  designated Accuracy’s
Bruno Husson as an independent expert to report on the financial
conditions of  Solvay SA (SOLB) ’s tender offer for Rhodia shares, the
company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
